Class UserSearchResultFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
      • com.example.shoutout.activity.fragment.UserSearchResultFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, androidx.savedstate.SavedStateRegistryOwner

    public class UserSearchResultFragment
extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
    Small fragment that shows a user-based result from a search. The information displayed consists of the following:
    • Avatar
    • Display name
    • Username

    April 29, 2021
